---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
description: Straight talk on missed calls, AI receptionists, and getting more out of every lead — from 406 Front Desk in Kalispell, Montana.
pageCss: post
permalink: /blog/
---
<section class="bloglist">
  <div class="bloglist-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Blog</div>
    <h1 class="bloglist-title">The 406 Front Desk Blog</h1>
    <p class="bloglist-sub">Straight talk on missed calls, AI receptionists, and getting more out of every lead — no hype, from a Montana company that builds them.</p>
    <div class="post-list">
      {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
      <a class="post-card" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="post-card-meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }} &middot; Read &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
